      • setAction

        public IPSecVPNPolicyRule.Builder setAction(java.lang.String action)
        Possible values are:
        • IPSecVPNPolicyRule.ACTION_PROTECT
        • IPSecVPNPolicyRule.ACTION_BYPASS
        PROTECT - Protect rules are defined per policy based IPSec VPN session. BYPASS - Bypass rules are defined per IPSec VPN service and affects all policy based IPSec VPN sessions. Bypass rules are prioritized over protect rules. This property may be present in responses from the server, but if it is present in a request to server it will be ignored.
        Parameters:
        action - New value for the property.
